      <title>历史经验表明，风险最高的股票在派对开始前上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/riskiest-stocks-jump-as-history-says-get-in-before-parties-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，股市风险最高的角落变得火爆，小型股罗素 2000 指数即将创下三年来首次收盘纪录。华尔街的传言称，交易员们可能发现了一些什么。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/riskiest-stocks-jump-as-history-says-get-in-before-parties-start</guid>
