      <title>阿根廷 ETF 流入量创纪录，因交易商买入 Milei 的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/argentina-etf-sees-record-inflows-as-traders-buy-milei-s-efforts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着华尔街支持阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 抑制通货膨胀和扭转多年来普遍存在的预算赤字的努力，追踪阿根廷股票的交易所交易基金出现了创纪录的资金流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/argentina-etf-sees-record-inflows-as-traders-buy-milei-s-efforts</guid>
